<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-45-1006 </DOCNO><TEXT>Sonography and computed tomography were the first imaging methods enablingthe visualisation of intramurally growing tumours of the stomach. Thearticle reports on a rare case of a diffuse leiomyoma that was diagnosedby means of computed tomography.</TEXT></DOC>